change_tag.brief: Change up to 2 tags of current NSFW Playlist. (e.g. 'prefix_herealiases_here yuri tentacle')

change_page.brief: Change page of current NSFW Playlist. Page is automatically increased when current paage is completed. (e.g. 'prefix_herealiases_here 4')

change_timeInterval.brief: Adjust the randomizing amount of seconds between images. Min=8, Max=180, Min-distance=20. (e.g. 'prefix_herealiases_here 10 25')
